@model CaregiverLite.Models.GroupChatModel



@using (Html.BeginForm("CreateNewGroup", "Chatting", FormMethod.Post, new { @id = "frmCreateGroup", @class = "horizontal-form", @enctype = "multipart/form-data" }))
{
    <div id="main_div">
        <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissable" style="display:none" id="dvError3">
            <button onclick="divClose();" class="close" type="button">×</button>
            <label id="lblError3"></label>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="form-group">
                @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.QuickBloxIds)
                @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.GroupDialogId)
                @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.MembersUserId)
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Group Name</label>
                    <span style="color:red;">*</span>
                    @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.GroupName)
                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.GroupName, new { @type = "text", @maxlength = "25", @placeholder = "", @class = "form-control" })
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Subject</label>
                    <span style="color:red;">*</span>
                    @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.GroupSubject)
                    @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.GroupSubject, new { @type = "text", @placeholder = "", @class = "form-control", @onblur = "javascript:IsGroupNameAndSubjectExist();" })
                </div>

                @if (Session["Role"].ToString() == "SuperAdmin" || Session["Role"].ToString() == "Scheduler" || Session["Role"].ToString() == "Admin")
                {
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="control-label">Office</label>
                        <span style="color:red;">*</span>
                        @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => Model.OfficeId)
                        @Html.DropDownList("OfficeId", (System.Web.Mvc.SelectList)ViewBag.lstOffice, "Select Office", new { @class = "form-control" })
                    </div>
                }
                else
                {
                    @Html.Hidden("OfficeId", "0")

                    @*@Html.HiddenFor(model => model.OfficeId,"0")*@
                }
            </div>
            @*<div class="form-group">
                    <label>Member</label>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <Select id="ddlMember" class="chosen-select" name="ddlMember" multiple="multiple">
                            @if (ViewBag.MemberList != null)
                            {
                                foreach (var item in ViewBag.MemberList)
                                {
                                    <option value="@item.UserId" nurseid="@item.NurseId" qbid="@item.QuickBloxId" email="@item.Email"> @item.Name </option>
                                }
                            }
                        </Select>
                    </div>
                </div>*@
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <button type="button" onclick="Next()" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary pull-right">Next</button>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
        <div id="main_div2" style="display:none">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Member</label>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <Select id="ddlMember" class="chosen-select" name="ddlMember" multiple="multiple">
                            @if (ViewBag.MemberList != null)
                            {
                                foreach (var item in ViewBag.MemberList)
                                {
                                    <option value="@item.UserId" qbid="@item.QuickBloxId" email="@item.Email"> @item.Name </option>
                                }
                            }
                        </Select>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <button type="button" onclick="CreateNewGroup()" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary pull-right">Create Group</button>
                <button type="button" onclick="gotoAddScreen1()" style="margin-right:5px" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary pull-right" tabindex="17">@CaregiverLite.Views.Resources.PatientRequest.ButtonPrevious</button>

                <div class="clearfix"></div>
            </div>

        </div>

}


<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/themes/base/jquery-ui.css">
<script type="text/javascript">

